<br>
Why HE is angry, I don't know.  If I was in another country, I would have been embarassed for making these people jump through hoops and causing them frustration because I cannot speak their language.<br>
<br>
You think that is all? Nope..... We finally get into my brand new car to drive down the street to get something to eat.  When making a left turn from the turn lane onto another street out of fucking no where this guy makes a right turn onto the same street and cuts right over into the lane I was in.  This lousy mexican almost hits me and I swerve to avoid him, causing people behind me to slam on their breaks and swerve out of the way also.  I had the green arrow light, so it was fucking definatly my turn to turn.  THE EXACT SAME MEXICAN WHO MY G/F HAD TO DEAL WITH EARLIER.  You think it ends there?  NO!  He then fucking pulls into the opposite lane of traffic and waits for the far lane to clear up.  I am saying, he fucking goes over the double yellows as in he is facing north in the south lane.  This moron is using the other lane of traffic as a &quot;turn lane.&quot;  Thank god no one was in that lane or it would be a head on.  He finally makes it into &quot;K-mart.<br>
<br>
(QUESTION)<br>
<br>
Why the fuck do I want these people in my country?  Try not to just call me &quot;net names&quot; or &quot;racist.&quot;  Explain to me why it is worth it.  Why is it worth all of the money I pay in taxes?  Don't try to tell me they don't get anything, DSHS has a program in our state where illegal aliens get $ 1,300 a month if they are a family of six.   <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/bvazaellecommunitycenter.showUserPublicProfile?gid=ammelen>Ammelen</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>I Live Here</span><br>  Posts: 2083<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(9/23/03 11:00 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fvazaellecommunitycenterfrm30.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=198.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: You guys wonder why I am racist, here is why.</span><hr size=1> Well, it sounds like we don't want this particular guy in our country.  The point is that he isn't an asshole because he's Mexican.  He's an asshole because he's an asshole.<br>
